[% META title = "Apiary Management System" %]
[% PageVersion = 'BMaster/apiary.tt,v 0.03 2026/03/17 shanta Exp shanta' %]
[% IF debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="app-container">

    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Apiary Management System</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">A comprehensive overview of your beekeeping operation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="content-primary">

            <div class="app-section">
                <p>This system is designed to provide you with a comprehensive overview of your beekeeping operation. It allows you to track, manage, and plan your apiary activities effectively.</p>

                [% IF no_data %]
                    <div class="empty-state">
                        <p>No yards have been added yet. <a href="/BMaster/add_yard" class="btn btn-primary">Please add a Yard</a> to get started.</p>
                    </div>
                [% ELSE %]
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Operation Overview</h2>
                        <p>Start your beekeeping day by reviewing your yard and hive data below. The system tracks changes in the number of frames of bees, brood, and other elements over the course of the season to help you understand the dynamics of your apiary at a glance.</p>
                        <p><em>Note: Interactive graph display requires the data visualization service to be running.</em></p>
                    </div>
                [% END %]
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Key Features</h2>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h3>Hive Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Monitor various aspects of your hives, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Hive condition and temperament</li>
                        <li>Number of bees and frames of brood</li>
                        <li>Frames of honey, foundation, comb, and empty</li>
                        <li>Weight, disease status, and internal temperature</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h3>Inventory Management</h3>
                    <p>Keep track of your apiary equipment inventory to plan what is needed for your next yard visit:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tops, brood boxes, entrance reducers</li>
                        <li>Frames, bottom boards, inner covers, frame feeders</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="content-section">
                    <h3>Seasonal Calendar</h3>
                    <p>Plan your activities for the season with our integrated calendar. Schedule and manage tasks effectively across all yards and hives.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Navigate Your Apiary</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/Apiary/QueenRearing">Queen Rearing System</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/yards">Your Yards</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="page-footer">
                <div class="footer-actions">
                    <a href="/BMaster" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to BMaster Home</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>
